muros (0.9.20) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial setup wizard: the Next button no longer silently does nothing. It
    used to submit every step at once against the in-memory model, so required
    fields belonging to later steps failed validation while the dialog was
    suppressed. Next now validates and stores only the current step and shows
    the validation dialog, so the user gets feedback and can move forward.
  * Web UI sidebar: moved the account block (user@host and Logout) to the bottom
    of the menu so the logo sits at the very top, removed the wasted left and top
    spacing, and aligned the brand, menu and account to the left edge.

